column5: Might be heading up to minden this week and was wondering if there was any ice on cedar. Any help would be greatly appreciated. Thanks jeff
Drove by on Saturday and was covered under the snow
Is there a fair bit of snow up there right now?
Hardly any around me was why i was wondering, thanks!
Only 1 spot on that ice seems to get fished ... Driven by it  hundreds of times
Yes in the deeper hole. All i have got from that spot is wormy perch and 1 nice largemouth. Hoping i can grt up there on thurs.
